Advantage of using test Automation framework

1. Reusability
2. Enhancing Reporting
3. parallel Execution
4. cross-browser testing
5. Modularity
6. Scalability
7. Maintenance
--- built-in frameworks
1. pytest
2. Unittest
3. robot framework

--custom framework
1. data driven framework
2. Keyword driven
3. hybrid framework (we use)

-----design----
name of project
       |
       POM(packages)
       |
       test_cases(packages)
       |
       utilities(packages)
       |
       test_data(folder)
       |
       logs(folder)
       |
       configurations
       |
       screenshots(folder)
       |
       reports(folder)
       |
       run.bat


